CheckoutDiscountCalculate - Class in com.pizzaserver.domain.model
Class called by CheckoutCalculate, it's used to calculate discounts of order and final cost after discounts discountHalfPrice - true if order has 2 pizzas (discount type 1) discountFreeDrink - true if order has 2 pizzas and drink - results in free drink (combines with discountHalfPrice) discountRealDeal - true if order is over 100zł - results in order cheaper by 20% of its price pizzaCount - pizzas count discountHPlist - list of products with HalfPrice discount OrderListProduct - discountFDid totalCost - order total cost before discount totalCostDiscount - order total cost after discount
